citris - Circular Tetris
See COPYING for license information

INSTALLING

If CVS checkout, run "sh autogen.sh" first.
Run "./configure && make && make install" to install to /usr/local.
Run "dpkg-buildpackage -rfakeroot" to build debian packge.


ABOUT

Citris idea of a circular Tetris was not stolen, but after doing some
research I found out that it has already been done in some similar clones.

Here is a list of the ones I know of:

ct
Doug Partridge <dpartrid@lawson.appcomp.utas.edu.au>
http://www.comp.utas.edu.au/students/dpartrid/ct/
GPL, GTK/GNOME based
Web page seams to be broken

Ringtris
Mark Wutka <wutka@netcom.com>
http://www.town-usa.com/arcade/ringtris/
Java applet

Revolution
Sean O'Connor <sean@windowsgames.co.uk>
http://www.windowsgames.co.uk/revolutn.html
Commercial, shareware game for Windows


